author: astoriabluelegos
title: All insectoid sets are AWESOME!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
review: I loved this set beacause it has cool lights and sounds.  The wing and piece decorations look cool. It can even pick up energy orbs with its magnet.  This is one of only a few sets that come with the insectoid Queen.  Mine also came with a cool bug mask which I put on my M&M guy machine so he looks like an Insectoid!
